I"Þ<h2 id="user-stories">User Stories</h2>

<p>User stories follow this pattern:</p>

<div class="language-md highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>As a <span class="sb">`USER`</span>
When I <span class="sb">`DO SOMETHING`</span>
Then I <span class="sb">`EXPECT SOMETHING`</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Examples:</p>

<div class="language-md highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>As an admin
When I click on dashboard
Then I should be on "/admin/dashboard"
And I should see all users listed
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-md highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>As a guest user
When I visit "/password-reset"
And I fill in <span class="sb">`Email`</span> with "lauren@example.com"
And I click <span class="sb">`Submit`</span>

Then I should be redirected to "/password-confirmation"
And I should see instructions to enter my confirmation code
And I should have received a text message with a confirmation code

When I enter the confirmation code
And I fill in <span class="sb">`Password`</span> with <span class="sb">`password`</span>
And I fill in <span class="sb">`Password Confirmation`</span> with <span class="sb">`password`</span>
And I click "Submit"
Then I should be redirected to "/dashboard"
And I should be logged in
And my old password should no longer work for logging in
And my new password should work after logging out and logging back in
</code></pre></div></div>
